@startuml
!theme plain
autonumber

actor "Analista de Implantação" as User
participant "Vue.js App" as Vue
participant "Dashboard Handler (Go)" as Handler
participant "Dashboard Service (Go)" as Service
participant "Repository (Go)" as Repo
database "PostgreSQL" as DB

title Fluxo de Consulta de Métricas e Safras (Analytics)

User -> Vue : Seleciona Safra (ex: Janeiro/2026)
Vue -> Handler : GET /api/v1/dashboard?mes=1&ano=2026
activate Handler

Handler -> Service : GetAnalyticsPorSafra(1, 2026)
activate Service

Service -> Repo : BuscarProjetosComReunioes(1, 2026)
activate Repo

Repo -> DB : SELECT * FROM projetos JOIN reunioes...
activate DB
DB --> Repo : Lista de Projetos e Eventos
deactivate DB

Repo --> Service : slice []models.Projeto
deactivate Repo

note over Service
  **Processamento da Lógica de Negócio:**
  1. Filtra projetos com >= 1 reunião realizada.
  2. Calcula % de Ativação (Meta: 86%).
  3. Calcula Taxa de No-Show (Meta: <10%).
  4. Verifica se as metas foram atingidas.
end note

Service -> Service : calcularMetas(projetos)

Service --> Handler : DashboardDTO (JSON ready)
deactivate Service

Handler --> Vue : HTTP 200 OK (JSON Payload)
deactivate Handler

Vue -> Vue : Renderiza Gráficos (ApexCharts/Chart.js)
Vue --> User : Exibe Dashboard com Status das Metas

@enduml